FBIS4-10464 "drlat071_c_94006" FBIS-LAT-94-071 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 MEXICO Secretary Urges Resumption of Talks in Chiapas Secretary Urges Resumption of Talks in Chiapas PA1204222794 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 0430 GMT 12 Apr 94 PA1204222794 Mexico City XEW Television Network Spanish BFN [From the "24 Hours" newscast] [Text] In Mexico City, Social Development Secretary Carlos Rojas has said it is urgent that peace talks in Chiapas be resumed so that necessary aid can be channeled to Indian communities.
